Take down--------------------------------------------------
Imagine:---
Imagine bachcha to be taking down his Machine and you taking all this down on an email to Suza.
Hindi Meaning:---
neecha uttarna, 
If you take something down, you reach up and get it from a high place such as a shelf.
If you take down a structure, you remove each piece of it.
If you take down a piece of information or a statement, you write it down.
Sentences:---
Alberg took the portrait down from the wall...
Lexicon!:---
Check Out:---
Difference: "put down" (likh do) and "take down" (likh lo).
Difference: "put down" (living-being killed) and "take down" (non-living distroyed).
